BioGeneticsRx uses a simple cheek swab (buccal swab) that we ship you for free to collect the DNA sample that is painless and convenient. The swabs are then shipped back to our labs for analysis, where our trained professionals create your personalized report. Don’t waste anymore time take the first step and fill out the form.




