More Info About Cancer Genetics, Inc. (CGIX)

Cancer Genetics, Inc. develops, commercializes, and provides molecular and biomarker-based tests and services in the United States, India, and China. Its tests enable physicians to personalize the clinical management of each individual patient by providing genomic information to diagnose, monitor, and inform cancer treatment; and enable biopharmaceutical companies involved in oncology trials to select candidate populations and reduce adverse drug reactions by providing information regarding genomic factors influencing subject responses to therapeutics. The company was founded in 1999 and is based in Rutherford, New Jersey. View our full CGIX ticker page with ratings, news, and more.
 






 


